name: SAP InsideTrack
description: Join fellow SAP enthusiasts at SAP InsideTrack, a community-driven event where SAP professionals and developers share insights, latest trends, and best practices. Engage in interactive sessions, hands-on workshops, and networking opportunities with experts from around the world.

name: SAP Community MeetUp
description: Connect with SAP professionals, developers, and business leaders at the SAP Community MeetUp. This event fosters collaboration, knowledge-sharing, and discussions on cutting-edge SAP technologies. Don't miss the chance to expand your network and gain valuable insights!

name: ABAP Workshops
description: Enhance your SAP ABAP skills with expert-led workshops designed for developers of all levels. Dive into coding best practices, advanced debugging techniques, and new innovations in ABAP development. Gain hands-on experience and practical knowledge to boost your SAP projects.
